source: TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_SEQ_00<tab>Ivaurault has information to share regarding your investigation.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_SEQ_00<tab>フォールゴウドの山師イヴォローは、冒険者に告白したいことがあるようだ。

source: TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_SEQ_01<tab>Ivaurault reveals that he has also seen the winged eyeball. The sighting took place at the rocky area to the west. Take yourself there and investigate.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_SEQ_01<tab>山師イヴォローは、目玉の化け物を目撃したらしい。西の岩場の<var 28 ((EObj)) F61E8C3E01 /var>付近を調査して、現れた魔物を倒そう。

source: TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_SEQ_02<tab>Instead of the winged eyeball, a monstrous banemite appears, and you are forced to defend yourself. Return to Fallgourd Float and report to Ivaurault.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_SEQ_02<tab><var 28 ((BNpcName)) F207C101 /var>が現れたが、「目玉の化け物」は現れなかった。フォールゴウドの「イヴォロー」に報告しよう。

source: TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_SEQ_03<tab>You learn that the banemite you slew had long been a scourge upon the locals. While Ivaurault is duly impressed with your skill at arms, he wonders whether he only imagined seeing the winged eyeball.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_SEQ_03<tab>冒険者が倒したのは、山師の間で恐れられていた凶悪な魔物だったらしい。しかし、イヴォローが見た「目玉の化け物」ではなかった。彼の見間違いだったのだろうか？
TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_TODO_00<tab>指定地点を調査して魔物を討伐

source: TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_IVAURAULT_000_000<tab>There is something you should know. I have been keeping this to myself, lest I worsen Medrod's paranoia, but I, too, have seen the winged eyeball.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_IVAURAULT_000_000<tab>ああ、やっと誰かに話すことができます。
メドロドを余計に怯えさせると思い、黙っていたのですが、
実は……僕も「目玉の化け物」を見たのです！

source: TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_IVAURAULT_000_001<tab>I cannot say whether it was coincidence, but my sighting took place precisely the same time as Medrod's. I was heading home after a day of digging when a shadow fell over me.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_IVAURAULT_000_001<tab>ちょうど、メドロドが化け物を見たのと同じころ……
作業終了の鐘を聞いて帰ろうとした僕の前に、
ふっと影が落ちました。

source: TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_IVAURAULT_000_002<tab>Looking up, I found myself locked in a gaze with a giant eyeball. I let out a scream at the top of my lungs and ran without once looking back. This happened at the rocky area west of here, in case you had a mind to investigate.
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_IVAURAULT_000_002<tab>見上げると、ギョロリとした目が僕を睨んでいたのです！
思わず悲鳴をあげて、一目散ですよ……。
もう化け物がいないか、西の岩場を見てきてくれませんか？

source: TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_DUMMY_000_010<tab>(/lookout at rocky area and slay the spider that pops.)
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_DUMMY_000_010<tab>（採掘場の近くの指定地点で「見渡す」
　強雌蜘蛛ポップ）

source: TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_IVAURAULT_000_020<tab>A monstrous banemite appeared...and you slew it!? That creature had long been a scourge upon the folk of Fallgourd!
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_IVAURAULT_000_020<tab>えっ……西の岩場に、
「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F207C101 /var>」が現れたんですか？
そいつは屈強な山師も震えあがる、凶悪な魔物なんですよ！？

source: TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_IVAURAULT_000_021<tab>Intentional or no, you have done us a great service. You have my gratitude!
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_IVAURAULT_000_021<tab>まさか倒しちゃうだなんて……。
さすがは冒険者、すごいですねぇ！

source: TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_IVAURAULT_000_022<tab>...But this does make me wonder, was it truly a winged eyeball I saw? Or merely a trick of light combined with blind panic?
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA802_00786_IVAURAULT_000_022<tab>……でも、おかしいな。
たしかに「目玉の化け物」を見たと思ったのに……
まさか、僕の見間違いだったのでしょうか？
